This paper deals with the security implications of cache algorithms, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also presents a novel approach for reasoning about the security of cache algorithms, which involves analyzing their behavior and performance (cs.PL). Additionally, the paper discusses the impact of cache algorithms on computer architecture (cs.AR) and software engineering (cs.SE). Finally, the paper's focus on analyzing cache algorithms and their behavior aligns with the systems and control (cs.SY) sub-category.
